Va bu mavhum tushuncha emas,

00:06:06.260 --> 00:06:08.260
yani sizni undan ajratib turgan narsa

00:06:08.260 --> 00:06:10.260
yani boshqa odamdan ajratib turgan narsa teringizdir.

00:06:10.260 --> 00:06:14.260
